<p>MEX 10/2014 
</p>
<p><b>M&#233;xico  
</b></p>
<p> 
</p>
<p> 
</p>
<p><b>Arbitrary 
</b></p>
<p><b>detention;  
</b></p>
<p><b>Freedom of 
