<p>Alleged physical attack against a human rights lawyer and threats against him and the 
</p>
<p>non-governmental organization (NGO) he works for. According to the information 
</p>
<p>received, on 4 September 2014, Mr. Makhamajan Abdujaparov, who works for the 
</p>
<p>NGO Spravedlivost (&#8220;Justice&#8221;), was assaulted by a representative or an affiliate of the 
</p>
<p>State Committee on National Security (SCNS). It is alleged that shortly after Mr. 
</p>
<p>Abdujaparov filed a complaint with the police, an employee of Spravedlivost received 
</p>
