</b></p>
<p> 
</p>
<p>Alleged arbitrary detention and torture of seven farmers in Chin State, Myanmar. 
</p>
<p>According to the information received, between 28 and 31 August 2014, Myanmar 
</p>
<p>Army soldiers arrested and detained U Maung Sein, U Kyaw Aung, U Aye Hla, U 
</p>
<p>Aung Kyaw Hla, U Kyaw Myint Oo, U Aung So, and U Sanay Aung. They were 
</p>
<p>reportedly tortured while in detention, accused by the soldiers of being in contact with 
</p>
<p>the Chin National Army.  While the seven individuals were released on 5 September 
</p>
<p>2014 and filed a formal complaint before the Chin State Government, no investigation 
</p>
<p>has taken place into their cases and they fear reprisals for speaking publicly about 
</p>
<p>their ordeal. 
